<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="priorProvisions" id="ida987192b-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Prior Provisions</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">A prior section 2494 was renumbered <ref href="/us/usc/t10/s2491">section 2491 of this title</ref>.</p>
</note>
